## Z AI
* `app/`
    * `Core/`
        * `App.php` - Main application kernel that manages service providers and dependency injection
        * `Config.php` - Handles environment variables from .env file
        * `Container.php` - Dependency injection container for binding and resolving services
        * `Database.php` - PDO connection manager for database operations
        * `DB.php` - Static facade for the Query Builder
        * `Router.php` - HTTP request router for handling URL routing
    * `Domain/`
        * `Models/` - Contains domain entities representing business concepts
            * `ProductInterface.php` - Interface defining contract for all product types
            * `Product.php` - Abstract base class with common product properties and methods
            * `DvdProduct.php` - Concrete implementation for DVD products
            * `BookProduct.php` - Concrete implementation for Book products
            * `FurnitureProduct.php` - Concrete implementation for Furniture products
    * `Infrastructure/`
        * `Hydrators/` - Contains data transformation components
            * `ProductHydratorInterface.php` - Interface for product hydrators
            * `DvdProductHydrator.php` - Hydrator for creating DVD product instances from DB data
            * `BookProductHydrator.php` - Hydrator for creating Book product instances from DB data
            * `FurnitureProductHydrator.php` - Hydrator for creating Furniture product instances from DB data
            * `ProductHydratorRegistry.php` - Registry for managing product hydrators
        * `Factories/` - Contains object creation components
            * `ProductFactory.php` - Abstract factory for creating products
            * `DvdProductFactory.php` - Concrete factory for creating DVD products
            * `BookProductFactory.php` - Concrete factory for creating Book products
            * `FurnitureProductFactory.php` - Concrete factory for creating Furniture products
            * `ProductFactoryResolver.php` - Resolves appropriate factory based on product type
    * `Exceptions/`
        * `Handler.php` - Global exception handler for converting exceptions to HTTP responses
        * `NotFoundException.php` - Exception thrown when a resource is not found (404)
        * `ValidationException.php` - Exception thrown for input validation failures (422)
        * `DuplicateSkuException.php` - Exception thrown when attempting to use a duplicate SKU (409)
    * `Http/`
        * `Controllers/`
            * `ProductController.php` - Handles HTTP requests for product operations
        * `Requests/`
            * `StoreProductRequest.php` - Form request validation for storing products
    * `Providers/`
        * `ServiceProvider.php` - Abstract base class for service providers
        * `ProductServiceProvider.php` - Registers product-related services in the container
    * `Repositories/`
        * `ProductRepository.php` - Handles data access with polymorphic hydration
    * `Services/`
        * `ProductService.php` - Business logic layer for product operations
* `database/`
    * `database.sqlite` - SQLite database file
* `routes/`
    * `api.php` - API route definitions
* `public/`
    * `index.php` - Application entry point
    * `.htaccess` - Apache configuration for URL rewriting
* `.env` - Environment configuration file
* `composer.json` - PHP package dependencies configuration
* `README.md` - Project documentation